snippet.title: IDate Trailer
snippet.description:
iDate, the first online interactive dating game, infuses your casual dating experience with music, dance and competition. Find your match on the dance floor and groove your way into love!

Official Website:
http://idate.ph.gameclub.com/main/idmain.asp

Official Facebook Page:
http://www.facebook.com/iDateOnlinePhilippines
